{"id":7936,"name":null,"username":"Battler","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png","created_at":"2005-01-03T10:23:18.000Z","cooked":"<p>OK. I got some information about this file.</p>\n<p>As we all know, it has only one entry.</p>\n<p>But this entry has actually 3 entries itself:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>An animation sequence or what. Mostly pixel data.</li>\n<li>The texts of the credits.</li>\n<li>A bitmap image, or maybe GIF. Probably means something.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>So maybe I can make a program to change the texts in the file, what do you think? And maybe in the future, bitmaps too.</p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T15:22:24.221Z","reply_count":17,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":90.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7933,"topic_slug":"the-lba2-hqr-file","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"OK. I got some information about this file.\n \nAs we all know, it has only one entry.\n \nBut this entry has actually 3 entries itself:\n1. An animation sequence or what. Mostly pixel data.\n2. The texts of the credits.\n3. A bitmap image, or maybe GIF. Probably means something.\n \nSo maybe I can make a program to change the texts in the file, what do you think? And maybe in the future, bitmaps too.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1016,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":fa