{"id":206374,"name":null,"username":"xesf","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/xesf/{size}/122_2.png","created_at":"2005-01-03T20:14:30.000Z","cooked":"<p>This file doenst have just 3 things inside, actually it have 90.</p>\n<p>(3 offsets indexs with 32 bits + 0x0198 bytes of empty data ) * 30</p>\n<p>All data before are just index to all this things:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>=&gt; Credits.</li>\n<li>=&gt; Shadding pallete image.<br>\n388. =&gt; 26 models and 60 animations.<br>\n8990. =&gt; Unknown</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom only-emoji\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:12:08.616Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":5.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7933,"topic_slug":"the-lba2-hqr-file","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1016,"username":"Battler","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"This file doens't have just 3 things inside, actually it have 90.\n\n(3 offsets indexs with 32 bits + 0x0198 bytes of empty data ) * 30\n\nAll data before are just index to all this things:\n\n1. =&gt; Credits. \n2. =&gt; Shadding pallete image.\n3....88. =&gt; 26 models and 60 animations.\n89...90. =&gt; Unknown...\n\n\n;)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator"