{"id":206832,"name":null,"username":"Battler","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png","created_at":"2005-01-06T13:21:41.000Z","cooked":"<p>OK. But is there any character, which I can use for identifying, whether an item is a body or an anim?</p>\n<p>Edit: BTW, I found out, what the first item is. It specified, how many item sets are init (1 item set = 198h null bytes and 12 offset bytes, starting from offset 3h on (the first item is this thing, and its not an item)). So, if you want to add 1 item, you must add 1 item set with 198h null bytes, and 12 offset bytes, and set the last 8 bytes to null (0h). Got it?</p>","post_number":18,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:12:24.403Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7933,"topic_slug":"the-lba2-hqr-file","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1016,"username":"Battler","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"OK. But is there any character, which I can use for identifying, whether an item is a body or an anim?\n \nEdit: BTW, I found out, what the first item is. It specified, how many item sets are init (1 item set = 198h null bytes and 12 offset bytes, starting from offset 3h on (the first item is this thing, and it's not an item)). So, if you want to add 1 item, you must add 1 item set with 198h null bytes, and 12 offset bytes, and set the last 8 bytes to null (0h). Got it?","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1016,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/the-lba2-hqr-file/7933/18","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
