{"id":248127,"name":null,"username":"Battler","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png","created_at":"2006-04-27T01:47:52.000Z","cooked":"<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"alexfont\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n alexfont:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This file doenst have just 3 things inside, actually it have 90.</p>\n<p>(3 offsets indexs with 32 bits + 0x0198 bytes of empty data ) * 30</p>\n<p>All data before are just index to all this things:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>=&gt; Credits.</li>\n<li>=&gt; Shadding pallete image.<br>\n388. =&gt; 26 models and 60 animations.<br>\n8990. =&gt; Unknown</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom only-emoji\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Correction:<br>\n0000h: Number of character (personage) blocks;</p>\n<p>NOTE: Each character block is 0198h empty (char. 00h) bytes + 3 32-bit offsets in the end.</p>\n<p>0004h: Offset of credits text;<br>\n0008h: Offset of shading palette image;</p>\n<p>000Ch-(Offset of credits text - 4): Character blocks of 01A4h bytes = 0198h empty + 0Ch (12 * 32-bits = 12 * 4 bytes) of the offsets in the end.</p>\n<p>The size of each item must be get by (offset of next item - offset of current item), except for the last time, where its size is (complete LBA2.HQR-entry file size - offset of current item).</p>\n<p>In the credits text, the characters 2Ah 00h 00h are used for line break, followed by either -, + or &gt; for colors. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":22,"post_type":1,"posts_count":22,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:37:22.247Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":6,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7933,"topic_slug":"the-lba2-hqr-file","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":463,"username":"xesf","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/xesf/{size}/122_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"\n[quote=\"alexfont\"]\nThis file doens't have just 3 things inside, actually it have 90.\n\n(3 offsets indexs with 32 bits + 0x0198 bytes of empty data ) * 30\n\nAll data before are just index to all this things:\n\n1. =&gt; Credits. \n2. =&gt; Shadding pallete image.\n3....88. =&gt; 26 models and 60 animations.\n89...90. =&gt; Unknown...\n\n\n;)\n[/quote]\nCorrection:\n0000h: Number of character (personage) blocks;\n\nNOTE: Each character block is 0198h empty (char. 00h) bytes + 3 32-bit offsets in the end.\n\n0004h: Offset of credits text;\n0008h: Offset of shading palette image;\n\n000Ch-(Offset of credits text - 4): Character blocks of 01A4h bytes = 0198h empty + 0Ch (12 * 32-bits = 12 * 4 bytes) of the offsets in the end.\n\nThe size of each item must be get by (offset of next item - offset of current item), except for the last time, where its size is (complete LBA2.HQR-entry file size - offset of current item).\n\n\nIn the credits text, the characters 2Ah 00h 00h are used for line break, followed by either -, + or &gt; for colors. ;)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1016,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/the-lba2-hqr-file/7933/22","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
